**10. Conclusion**

The Smart City Complaint Analysis project successfully identified complaint trends, service bottlenecks, and recurring civic issues. The insights obtained from the analysis can help city authorities improve operational efficiency, reduce complaint resolution time, and enhance overall citizen satisfaction.

